sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor User as Customer / Driver
  participant App as User App
  participant Gateway as API Gateway
  participant Support as Support/Admin API
  participant Ride as Ride Service
  participant Payment as Payment Service
  participant Review as Review Service
  participant Notification as Notification Service
  actor Admin
  User->>App: Submit complaint with ride/payment evidence
  App->>Gateway: POST /api/support/complaints
  Gateway->>Support: Create complaint
  Support->>Ride: Verify requester belongs to ride
  Ride-->>Support: Ride summary
  Support->>Payment: Load payment context
  Payment-->>Support: Payment summary
  Support->>Review: Load review/rating context
  Review-->>Support: Review summary
  Support-->>App: Complaint created
  Admin->>Support: Review complaint and choose action
  alt Refund or payment adjustment
    Support->>Payment: Create refund/adjustment request
    Payment-->>Support: Payment action result
  else Warning or account action
    Support->>Ride: Attach resolution note
    Ride-->>Support: Case evidence updated
  end
  Support->>Notification: Send resolution notification
  Notification-->>User: Complaint result
